item.dc:creator: @gothic_queen casey.
item.description:
@gothic_queen wrote:

[quote=“Xx R A G 3 R, post:5, topic:251619”]TIER 1 MEMBERS:
110+ F2P Combat, 1400+ Total

im 109 f2p but i have over 1400 total do you guys do pvp events?
if i decide to join a clan i kind of want a friendly community + a clan that daily has events sounds like this clan has those i might just look into joining :)[/quote]
We even it out usually.
We have f2p leaders and p2p leaders. They each decide on their own events, but the p2p staff has to make at least 3 events with p2p in f2p a week.

So one of the DPT(Drop party team) has confirmed next week’s drop at 230M, though it will be p2p. Now the next drop will be f2p.[br][br][size=1]Posted on: December 21, 2008, 11:05:14 am[/size][hr][quote=“R.I.P RSC, post:6, topic:251619”]I hope there are more tiers then the 4 you listed, because the gap between 4 and 3 is too big. I have a level ~85 which means I get in level 4, and I’ll be hanging around with people that are level 3.

Not that I’ll join though, I quit RS long ago. Just giving my opinion.[/quote]
When we look at you application, we would see this and probably bump you up. Tbh, tiers don’t even matter except for higher levels.
